<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM11.6.4">
<l>paṉipparavait tiraitatumpap pārellām neṭuṅkaṭalē yāṉakālam</l>
<l>iṉikkaḷaika ṇivarkkillai yeṉṟulaka mēḻiṉaiyu mūḻilvāṅki</l>
<l>muṉittalaivaṉ muḻaṅkoḷicēr tiruvayiṟṟil vaittummai yuyyakkoṇṭa</l>
<l>kaṉikaḷavat tiruvuruvat toruvaṉaiyē kaḻaltoḻumā kallīrkaḷē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Learn how to worship the anklets of the one</l>
<l rend="indent">whose divine appearance is of the blueberry fruit,</l>
<l>The lord of sages who took you to save [you],</l>
<l rend="indent">placing [you] in his divine stomach with clapping lightning,</l>
<l>Having taken the seven worlds in turn, thinking,</l>
<l rend="indent">“Now there is no protector for them,”</l>
<l>At the time that all of the earth had become a vast sea</l>
<l rend="indent">so that waves swelled in the cold expanse.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
